{"tid":1780271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好多經濟圏Post都因為\"偽黃\"或\"無商會認證\"就Ban，有無得簡化認證？","createTime":"2019-12-12T08:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:48:16.000Z","uid":135332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d47e624da1ac1eda0bd1d3f7ea5e4e4421de47af","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"商會/公司/民主認證呢d野全部長遠都要搞，但目前因為未有人搞，<span style=\"color: purple;\">好多行動post就因為 &quot;有人偽黃&quot; 或 &quot;無商會認證&quot; 就ban哂</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">其實，可唔可以簡化下 d steps，商店證明到佢有聘請好多手足 / 定期捐錢星火 (貼文宣果d自行衡量)，我本人其實都支持，不理背後動機。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">相信消費者眼光，況且消費完先發現係偽黃，最多下次唔消費，唔好因為有機會去錯偽黃店而拖慢經濟圏運作，Believe in the wisdom of crowds!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n時勢緊迫，我地目前未必需要一套<span style=\"color: purple;\">超完善的黃藍認證系統</span> (依然是long term goal)，其實<span style=\"color: red;\">只需要俾消費者知道呢間鋪頭做左d咩/捐左咩錢，留番消費者自行判斷</span>啦!<br />\n<br />\n否則樣樣野都等另一樣野搞好先做，咁樣我地黃色經濟效率咪<span style=\"color: blue;\">仲慢過常日開會的政府</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？ 我地又無大台。"},{"pid":"6e1eae6187b1a00c986c4f73fe3f76ee71fc5d7d","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7570edb0999e09609a90b2a9d07562e2f4acc28","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"精明消費者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef3f1317bbcc7e43fa4790920c5df4047f73be","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"暫時大部份黃店消費都不是貴價名牌野，又唔係手足條命，的確唔好為 &quot;商會認證&quot; 嘈來嘈去。<br />\n<br />\n支持多做實事。"},{"pid":"3ca1342950c45ffb12a2433105d9ca747286d8ca","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c9f476dac57989808d22e629f22f5dc42688110","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"香港人多，消息傳得快，靠親朋好友口碑，我信消費者眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n證明到佢有聘請好多手足 / 定期捐錢星火，我本人支持。"},{"pid":"898c417a5698cf6872f8525645c2cd57fe949cf2","tid":1780271,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"Believe in the wisdom of crowds! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8c2aeb1392167d2d5755ff5d2ed034b65822c3","tid":1780271,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f269a090fca0e4cbc5a9175802926aaad042c6","tid":1780271,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a125f778f91fee7d0114cbe3646a5e083d125db8","tid":1780271,"uid":336769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ddc64b5c4bb387c0973b304056061ef0244fbfd","tid":1780271,"uid":135332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}